reviewText: The title of this DVD alone should be enough to tell all people to avoid this.  This is boring even for little kids.  The characters are completely out-of-character, and everything is so sugarcoated that it makes your skin crawl.  Little kids get bored when this show is on.  This is an insult to children's intelligence and a disgrace to the Looney Tunes creators.
